WEBVTT

00:00.165 --> 00:01.702
Previously on The Fosters...

00:01.712 --> 00:03.167
The T cells didn't work.

00:03.177 --> 00:05.178
You can do another
round of gene therapy.

00:05.188 --> 00:06.965
I don't want any more treatment.

00:06.975 --> 00:09.877
When the time comes,
you should let me go.

00:09.887 --> 00:11.346
<i>I don't know why I didn't just</i>

00:11.357 --> 00:13.247
get back with Aaron
when I had the chance.

00:13.257 --> 00:15.449
He said he's taking it
slow with that girl Amanda.

00:15.459 --> 00:16.616
I'm ready to be with you

00:16.626 --> 00:18.284
if you still want to.

00:18.294 --> 00:20.687
GRAY: Mr. Snow's the one
that's been doing the harassing

00:20.697 --> 00:21.834
of Patrick Molloy.

00:21.845 --> 00:24.123
I find it very interesting
that you're still in contact

00:24.133 --> 00:26.433
<i>with a pedophile you say
hasn't committed a crime.</i>

00:26.444 --> 00:29.361
I need to get these requests for search
warrants over to Judge Walderman.

00:29.372 --> 00:31.064
Who wants to see the
makeover we gave Jude?

00:31.074 --> 00:32.821
LENA: <i>Talking about hitting it</i>

00:32.832 --> 00:35.004
and asking what's your
favorite position is not funny.

00:35.015 --> 00:36.602
I talked to Declan, and he's out

00:36.612 --> 00:38.144
so Eminent Power is dropping us.

00:40.315 --> 00:41.841
JUDGE: Mr. and Mrs. Sinfuego

00:41.851 --> 00:43.609
are to report to Immigration and Customs

00:43.619 --> 00:45.177
for immediate deportation.

00:45.187 --> 00:47.212
What if we could get an ICE agent

00:47.222 --> 00:48.880
to testify on the Sinfuegos' behalf?

00:48.890 --> 00:49.914
No way.

00:49.924 --> 00:51.549
Then we're gonna compel you to testify.

00:51.559 --> 00:52.825
You've been served.

00:54.228 --> 00:56.762
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

00:58.619 --> 01:01.559
<i>♪ It's not where you come from ♪</i>

01:01.569 --> 01:04.929
<i>♪ It's where you belong ♪</i>

01:04.938 --> 01:07.631
<i>♪ Nothin' I would trade ♪</i>

01:07.641 --> 01:10.934
<i>♪ I wouldn't have it any other way ♪</i>

01:10.944 --> 01:13.504
<i>♪ You're surrounded ♪</i>

01:13.514 --> 01:16.272
<i>♪ By love and you're wanted ♪</i>

01:16.282 --> 01:19.843
<i>♪ So never feel alone ♪</i>

01:19.853 --> 01:22.512
<i>♪ You are home with me ♪</i>

01:22.522 --> 01:24.622
<i>♪ Right where you belong ♪</i>

